snippet.title: First Splash
snippet.description:
The first demo for Sonic Essence will be at this year's Sonic Hacking Contest! This demo will have sonic's intro stage (Windmill Isle) and the first stage of his campaign (Seaside Splash).

See you then!
https ://shc.zone/

Music by @fungalfan99 
Trailer by @Aly_Style
